PrecisAppointment of ARTHUR B. TRUDEAU, of Aylmer, Quebec, as a temporary member of the Canadian International Trade Tribunal to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending December 31, 1997, effective January 1, 1997, and order that ARTHUR B. TRUDEAU shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act.
